# OverLanguage workflow: verify and pay
workflow: VerifyPay
intent: verify artifact hash and issue payment receipt
step 1: index file → local_index
step 2: compute hash → merkle_root
step 3: verify hash ≡ canonical → verified
step 4: issue receipt → signed_receipt
artifact: signed_receipt
receipt: SHA256 chained from step 1 to step 4
value: verified artifact with payment proof
